<h2 class="dl__caption-title">
<a data-beacon='{"p": {"lnid": "dl-headline"}}' data-rapid_p="330" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:;cpos:80;slk:Americans still struggle to cope with these disasters;tar:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reference.com;tar_uri:%2Fslideshow%2Flargest-environmental-disasters-of-the-last-ten-years%2F%3Futm_source%3Daol%26utm_medium%3DP_AOL_CO_US_D_EnvironmentalDisasters%26utm_content%3Dnewnext%26utm_term%3Daol%26o%3D781823;ll1:674612015;mtest:;expb:;pos:2;elm:hdln;" href="https://www.reference.com/slideshow/largest-environmental-disasters-of-the-last-ten-years/?utm_source=aol&amp;utm_medium=P_AOL_CO_US_D_EnvironmentalDisasters&amp;utm_content=newnext&amp;utm_term=aol&amp;o=781823" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">Americans still struggle to cope with these disasters</a>
</h2>
<p class="dl__caption-copy">
<a data-beacon='{"p": {"lnid": "dl-copy"}}' data-rapid_p="331" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:;cpos:80;slk:Americans still struggle to cope with these disasters;tar:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reference.com;tar_uri:%2Fslideshow%2Flargest-environmental-disasters-of-the-last-ten-years%2F%3Futm_source%3Daol%26utm_medium%3DP_AOL_CO_US_D_EnvironmentalDisasters%26utm_content%3Dnewnext%26utm_term%3Daol%26o%3D781823;ll1:674612015;mtest:;expb:;pos:3;elm:copy;" href="https://www.reference.com/slideshow/largest-environmental-disasters-of-the-last-ten-years/?utm_source=aol&amp;utm_medium=P_AOL_CO_US_D_EnvironmentalDisasters&amp;utm_content=newnext&amp;utm_term=aol&amp;o=781823" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">Earthquakes, floods, and fires are the catastrophes most likely to devastate towns and their communities.</a>
</p>
<a class="dl__linkline" data-beacon='{"p": {"lnid": "dl-cta"}}' data-rapid_p="332" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:;cpos:80;slk:Americans still struggle to cope with these disasters;tar:https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reference.com;tar_uri:%2Fslideshow%2Flargest-environmental-disasters-of-the-last-ten-years%2F%3Futm_source%3Daol%26utm_medium%3DP_AOL_CO_US_D_EnvironmentalDisasters%26utm_content%3Dnewnext%26utm_term%3Daol%26o%3D781823;ll1:674612015;mtest:;expb:;pos:4;elm:rhdln;" href="https://www.reference.com/slideshow/largest-environmental-disasters-of-the-last-ten-years/?utm_source=aol&amp;utm_medium=P_AOL_CO_US_D_EnvironmentalDisasters&amp;utm_content=newnext&amp;utm_term=aol&amp;o=781823" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">The worst disaster of all time</a>
<span class="dl__caption-count">80/81</span>
</div><div aria-hidden="true" class="dl__caption slick-slide" data-slick-index="81" style="width: 210px; position: relative; left: -17010px; top: 0px; z-index: 998; opacity: 0;" tabindex="-1">
<div class="dl__sponsor">
<a class="dl__sponsor-name" data-rapid_p="333" href="http://mentalflare.com" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">Mental Flare</a>
</div>
<h2 class="dl__caption-title">
<a data-beacon='{"p": {"lnid": "dl-headline"}}' data-rapid_p="334" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:;cpos:81;slk:Guy dumps 2,000 lbs. of chemicals in his pool for crazy reason;tar:https%3A%2F%2Fmentalflare.com;tar_uri:%2Fgiant-pool-creation%2F%3Fas%3D708l1oa;ll1:174416087;mtest:;expb:;pos:2;elm:hdln;" href="https://mentalflare.com/giant-pool-creation/?as=708l1oa" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">Guy dumps 2,000 lbs. of chemicals in his pool for crazy reason</a>
</h2>
<p class="dl__caption-copy">
<a data-beacon='{"p": {"lnid": "dl-copy"}}' data-rapid_p="335" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:;cpos:81;slk:Guy dumps 2,000 lbs. of chemicals in his pool for crazy reason;tar:https%3A%2F%2Fmentalflare.com;tar_uri:%2Fgiant-pool-creation%2F%3Fas%3D708l1oa;ll1:174416087;mtest:;expb:;pos:3;elm:copy;" href="https://mentalflare.com/giant-pool-creation/?as=708l1oa" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">People were puzzled by this guy's  strange globe packed with  chemicals, until he dumped it in his  pool and they saw the wild effects.</a>
</p>
<a class="dl__linkline" data-beacon='{"p": {"lnid": "dl-cta"}}' data-rapid_p="336" data-ylk="ll2:amp-bon;aid:;cpos:81;slk:Guy dumps 2,000 lbs. of chemicals in his pool for crazy reason;tar:https%3A%2F%2Fmentalflare.com;tar_uri:%2Fgiant-pool-creation%2F%3Fas%3D708l1oa;ll1:174416087;mtest:;expb:;pos:4;elm:rhdln;" href="https://mentalflare.com/giant-pool-creation/?as=708l1oa" tabindex="-1" target="_blank">Too late</a>

        function isAolClient(){
  var userAgent = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase(),
  isOldAolClient = userAgent.indexOf('aol'),
  isAolSecure= userAgent.indexOf('aolsecure'),
  isNewAolClient = typeof window.external !== 'undefined'&& typeof window.external.jsWindow !== 'undefined' && typeof window.external.jsWindow.authState !== 'undefined' ? window.external.jsWindow.authState() : -1;
  return (isOldAolClient !== -1 || isNewAolClient !== -1) && isAolSecure == -1;
  }
